{"tid":106810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"家政婦偏頭痛　竟是蟑螂跑進頭骨作祟","createTime":"2017-02-04T03:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T04:55:29.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"df8173369f3c845211643e6b29edaf4f7f53c867","tid":106810,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T03:38:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170204/1048781/papersec_right\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20170204%2F1048781%2Fpapersec_right&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=52407432\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170204/1048781/papersec_right</a><br />\n2017年02月04日09:40 <br />\n<br />\n印度一名42歲家政婦希爾維(Selvi)日前感到頭非常痛，她感覺整顆頭好像要燒起來，之後醫師為她診治，竟發現是一隻蟑螂在作祟。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《每日郵報》報導，希爾維日前半夜驚醒，感到頭部非常疼痛，感覺有東西在她的頭裡亂動，而且痛到發熱，眼部也有灼熱感。她之後到醫院就診，醫生檢查發現，有一隻蟑螂就卡在她頭顱內部的兩眼之間。醫師花了45分鐘的手術，從希爾維的鼻中取出一隻活蟑螂，並相信就是這隻蟑螂在作祟，導致希爾維不舒服。醫師桑卡(Shankar)也說，這是他執業30年來，第一次看到這麼奇特的病例。<br />\n<br />\n桑卡也指出，如果希爾維沒有就醫、置之不理，讓蟑螂死在頭顱中，很可能導致腦部被細菌感染，狀況恐會更糟糕。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170204/640_6cd18da14b8d15cae0ec77ffef32628e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170204%2F640_6cd18da14b8d15cae0ec77ffef32628e.jpg&h=d4e87303&s={SIZE}\" />印度家政婦希爾維偏頭痛，就是這隻蟑螂跑進頭骨作祟。翻自《每日郵報》"},{"pid":"12d334a716b5a7ff01722420d0bb09982dcca502","tid":106810,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T03:40:11.000Z","msg":"曱甴死全家啦"},{"pid":"5398cfba3afa8f14623fa2c738e0e02ba50424a0","tid":106810,"uid":34209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T03:42:23.000Z","msg":"點入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de02eb4c4124334f3b6378a538b5aad841f229f1","tid":106810,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T04:44:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n耳鼻喉肛相通<br />\n條條大路通羅馬<br />\n是但一度既姐"},{"pid":"843b526ee6116cc0d05c6738a38e34d99150a867","tid":106810,"uid":35749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T04:55:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n耳鼻<span style=\"color: red;\">喉肛</span>相通<br />\n條條大路通羅馬<br />\n是但一度既姐</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}